<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Norman_Pearlstine" title="Norman Pearlstine">Norman Pearlstine</a> - editor-in-chief of <a href="/wiki/Time_(magazine)" title="Time (magazine)">Time</a> magazine from (1995-2005)</li>
